Algorithm:

1. Start
2. Input a positive number (num).
3. Initialize sum = 0.
4. Compute the sum of digits:
     •Set temp = num.
     •Repeat while temp > 0:
       -Extract the last digit using temp % 10.
       -Add it to sum.
       -Remove the last digit using temp / 10.
5. Display the sum of digits.
6. Check divisibility:
     •Set divisor = 2.
     •Repeat while divisor ≤ 9:
       -If num % divisor == 0, print that num is divisible by divisor.
       -Else, print that num is not divisible by divisor.
       -Increment divisor by 1.
7. End
